# Product Requirements Document (PRD)

## Product Name

Kulmis Academy

## Product Overview

Kulmis Academy is a modern e-learning platform designed to deliver high-quality online courses with a clean and engaging learning experience. The platform allows instructors (admins) to upload structured courses and lessons, while students can enroll in courses and watch lessons hosted on Vimeo.

The goal of the platform is to create a simple but powerful course-learning environment similar to Udemy or Coursera, where students can easily browse courses, enroll, and track their learning progress.

The system will be built using Next.js, Tailwind CSS, Neon PostgreSQL database, and Vimeo for secure video hosting.

---

# Technology Stack

Frontend Framework
Next.js (App Router)

Styling
Tailwind CSS

Database
Neon (Serverless PostgreSQL)

Video Hosting
Vimeo

Authentication
NextAuth or JWT authentication

Deployment
Vercel

