# UI Design Requirements

The platform must have a modern UI similar to Udemy or Coursera.

Design principles:

* Clean layout
* Responsive design
* Mobile friendly
* Smooth animations
* Minimalistic interface

Use Tailwind CSS components and reusable UI patterns.

---

# Video Player Experience

The lesson player should provide a distraction-free experience.

Requirements:

* Vimeo embedded player
* No download links
* Autoplay next lesson option
* Progress saved automatically

---

# Security Requirements

* Protect lesson pages for enrolled students only
* Secure authentication
* Prevent unauthorized access to course videos
* Hide Vimeo source links from users

---

# Performance Requirements

* Fast loading pages
* Optimized images
* Server-side rendering using Next.js
* Efficient database queries

---

# Future Features

The platform architecture should allow future additions such as:

* Quiz system
* Certificates
* Student notes
* Comments
* AI learning assistant
* Subscription payments

---

# Development Instructions

Generate a full-stack application with the following:

* Next.js App Router structure
* Tailwind CSS styling
* Neon PostgreSQL database integration
* Authentication system
* Admin dashboard
* Student dashboard
* Course and lesson management
* Vimeo video player integration

Ensure clean code structure, reusable components, and scalable architecture.
